Simplify $2a(2a^2 + a) - a^2$. ||| 
Simplifying, we have: 
\begin{align*} 
2a(2a^2 + a) - a^2 &= 2a \cdot 2a^2 + 2a \cdot a - a^2 \\
&= 4a^2 + 2a^2 - a^2 = \boxed{5a^2}. 
\end{align*}

